  "3200060": {
    "name": "与东风谷早苗的神风一起",
    "steam_appid": 3200060,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【语言相关说明】<br>－本作的界面（UI）支持切换为简体中文显示。 <br>－剧情对话文本（字幕）目前仅提供日语和英语版本。 <br>　如您获取并导入对应的简体中文文本文件，游戏内可正常显示简体中文字体。 <br>－语音（完全音频）仅提供日语配音。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/bd053a1bca5288920d5e024b35612a4b.avif?t=1766823405\" width=600 height=180 /></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《与东风谷早苗的神风一起》是一款以可爱的像素艺术绘制的东方二次创作2D动作游戏。  <br>主角东风谷早苗创造出了全新的奥义“符掠夺者”！  <br>凭借这股力量，她能够吸入途中遇到的妖怪，并将夺取的力量化为自己的符来操纵！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>奇怪！　袭击守矢神社的神秘黑影！！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守矢神社的主神——神奈子大人竟然遭到不明身份的袭击！？ <br>更有甚者，神社的象征——御柱也被盗走了！ <br>犯人究竟是惯常的黑白大盗魔理沙，还是可恨的商敌命莲寺，抑或是那位露出不敌笑容的天人……！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时而奔走于大地，时而翱翔于高空，目标直指妖怪之山的更高处！ <br>凭借“符掠夺者”从途中妖怪身上夺取的力量，夺回守矢神社的和平！！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>爽快！　秘技“符掠夺者”！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/PV_gif_steam01_640x360_fr30.GIF?t=1766823405\" /></span>在旅途中出现的妖怪，可以通过“符掠夺者”吸入，获得全新的符。<br>获得符的早苗会变身为与原妖怪相关的姿态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/61504ef86b97deab3c2b5bf62d6c5976.poster.avif?t=1766823405\" width=200 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/61504ef86b97deab3c2b5bf62d6c5976.webm?t=1766823405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由像素艺术描绘的早苗可爱身姿也值得关注！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>激走！　天狗流名竞走！！（TENGU-RUMEI-RACE）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/e91b45025ddffd64f15360bb1d798867.poster.avif?t=1766823405\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/e91b45025ddffd64f15360bb1d798867.webm?t=1766823405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/e91b45025ddffd64f15360bb1d798867.mp4?t=1766823405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏进程中解锁的竞速小游戏“天狗流名竞走”中，早苗将与魔理沙在充满怀旧乐曲的赛道上展开对决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胜利的关键在于如何精彩地驰骋于起伏激烈的山道。<br>如果能展现出华丽的跑姿，射命丸文会拍下照片并大力称赞！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/1d26e5d95c97cc4278a773479a787351.poster.avif?t=1766823405\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/1d26e5d95c97cc4278a773479a787351.webm?t=1766823405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/1d26e5d95c97cc4278a773479a787351.mp4?t=1766823405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>激战！　射击对决！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在关卡中，会有敌人向早苗发起空中战的挑战。<br>在空中战中，玩家可以纵横无尽地操纵早苗，享受射击游戏的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与平常战斗截然不同的妖怪弹幕战，需要借助神奈子大人的力量来突破！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/8dabc2d96bcaff74a837ac165fcf1fb5.poster.avif?t=1766823405\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/8dabc2d96bcaff74a837ac165fcf1fb5.webm?t=1766823405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/8dabc2d96bcaff74a837ac165fcf1fb5.mp4?t=1766823405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剧情竟然是全语音！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请尽情享受早苗与幻想少女们那些不受常识束缚的精彩对话吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■主要登场角色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/0c2d3ab40ac0fc56cf4c8c8838d54bf5.avif?t=1766823405\" width=120 height=135 /></span>・东风谷早苗（CV：白砂沙帆）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/63d1be184207590aed066cb732ba8ed9.avif?t=1766823405\" width=120 height=120 /></span>・雾雨魔理沙（CV：金澤まい）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/38f84fce53e8a0a24a06de18cc393b3f.avif?t=1766823405\" width=180 height=150 /></span>・八坂神奈子（CV：芝崎典子）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/f009977102e5e38ab75ce33e07ab664d.avif?t=1766823405\" width=140 height=120 /></span>・洩矢诹访子（CV：関口理咲）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/57c1ef2f1d41762a552c9ba7c6567fef.avif?t=1766823405\" width=120 height=120 /></span>・比那名居天子（CV：村田綾香）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200060/extras/c6504e7f1119fc999dcc971d613bbb36.avif?t=1766823405\" width=120 height=120 /></span>・射命丸文（CV：かなまいの友人I）</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>迫真！　迫力！　符卡战斗！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在剧情后半段，Boss 会使用符卡，开启手感十足的高难度模式。<br>让人联想到原作的弹幕，由早苗的“符掠夺者”来突破吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>安心！　安全！　微风模式！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开启“微风模式”后，受到的伤害将减半，并且还能从部分妖怪处取得回复道具。<br>如果你不擅长动作游戏，或者在强敌 Boss 面前陷入苦战，请启用此模式来帮助自己尽情游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※在 Boss 战期间无法切换 ON／OFF！<br>　失败后请在再战前，于选项中进行更改。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>配信・录制指南</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作的影像与音声可自由进行配信与录制。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请在标题或简介栏中明确标注正在游玩《与东风谷早苗的神风一起/ SANAE’s Sylphid Breeze》</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >禁止将游戏内素材用于商业或营利目的的再分发与加工。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许通过广告收入、打赏、赞助等方式进行收益化。</p></li></ul>",
